I can't believe I look like a panda.

01:03:46.677 --> 01:03:47.678
Where are you off to?

01:03:47.761 --> 01:03:50.055
I thought you knew everything.

01:03:50.139 --> 01:03:52.433
I hear Ms. Kim is going to Hyenam.
You, too?

01:03:53.183 --> 01:03:54.685
They both hate us, so no.

01:03:55.352 --> 01:03:57.771
I'm not telling you where I'm going.
Don't call me, okay?

01:03:58.772 --> 01:04:01.650
You're not going to tell me? Okay.

01:04:02.651 --> 01:04:05.737
You're just leaving now?
That's just disappointing.

01:04:05.821 --> 01:04:08.782
Wherever you're going,
you'll be back soon, anyway.

01:04:08.866 --> 01:04:10.951
- Huh?
- See you soon.

01:04:13.954 --> 01:04:15.164
But I...

01:04:15.247 --> 01:04:18.417
So, if I'm coming back...

01:04:18.500 --> 01:04:19.668
I...

01:04:21.795 --> 01:04:23.172
Gosh.

01:05:20.062 --> 01:05:21.188
Good work.

01:05:21.939 --> 01:05:23.815
Didn't I tell you

01:05:23.899 --> 01:05:26.026
I'd bring you back to Suojae
as soon as possible?

01:05:28.570 --> 01:05:29.571
Alright.

01:05:32.991 --> 01:05:33.992
Congratulations

01:05:35.619 --> 01:05:37.287
on your safe return, Mr. President.

01:05:42.793 --> 01:05:46.421
THE JUDGE RETURNS

01:06:25.294 --> 01:06:27.588
Sin-jin's rebellion has begun.

01:06:27.671 --> 01:06:29.172
Call a meeting at Suojae tonight.

01:06:29.256 --> 01:06:31.258
We'll get rid of it
if it looks problematic.

01:06:31.717 --> 01:06:33.302
I never trusted you from the start.

01:06:33.552 --> 01:06:34.928
You don't have anywhere to run.

01:06:35.012 --> 01:06:38.432
So, we'll have to give what Sin-jin wants.

01:06:38.682 --> 01:06:40.434
He killed a man!

01:06:40.517 --> 01:06:43.061
So, you approached me for me.

01:06:43.145 --> 01:06:44.646
I think I'm getting blamed.

01:06:45.022 --> 01:06:46.607
This is the last chance.

01:06:47.274 --> 01:06:48.483
It won't take long.

01:06:48.567 --> 01:06:50.777
I was ready to go all the way
when I started, anyway.

